Global cPDM in Automotive Market Insights
cPDM in Automotive Market size was valued at USD 5.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.5% from 2024 to 2030.

cPDM in Automotive Market Overview
The global cPDM (Collaborative Product Data Management) market in the automotive industry was valued at USD 9.42 billion in 2024 and is expected to reach USD 15.56 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% during the forecast period. The increasing need for innovation, improved product design, and compliance with regulatory standards are the primary factors driving the market's growth. Moreover, the growing demand for electric and autonomous vehicles is further accelerating the adoption of cPDM solutions. Key players in the industry include Dassault Systèmes, Siemens, and PTC, contributing significantly to market expansion.

